  <p>As part of the continued development of their online service, NHS 24 has recently introduced a facility to enable people to respond to NHS 24 via the feedback form on <a href="http://www.nhs24.com" target="_blank">www.nhs24.com</a>. The monitoring of the number of emails received through this channel began in January 2008 and figures are detailed in the following table:</p>

